meanings.sent1: The outfit she wore to the party was even tackier than the one she wore last week.
meanings.sent2: The decorations on the cake looked tackier than expected.
meanings.sent3: His attempt at singing was tackier than a cat yowling in the night.
meanings.sent4: The movie's special effects were tackier than a dollar store toy.
meanings.sent5: The smell in the old house was tackier than a wet dog in a small room.
